org.apache.flink.graph.drivers.transform

类 GraphKeyTypeTransform<VV,EV>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.graph.drivers.parameter.ParameterizedBase
      • org.apache.flink.graph.drivers.transform.GraphKeyTypeTransform<VV,EV>
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Parameterized, Transform<Graph<LongValue,VV,EV>,Graph<?,VV,EV>,DataSet<TranslatableResult<?>>,DataSet<TranslatableResult<?>>>

    public class GraphKeyTypeTransform<VV,EV>
extends ParameterizedBase
implements Transform<Graph<LongValue,VV,EV>,Graph<?,VV,EV>,DataSet<TranslatableResult<?>>,DataSet<TranslatableResult<?>>>
    Transform the ID type of graphs from LongValue to byte, short, char, integer, float, double, or string. Both boxed Java types and Flink Value types are supported. The result is transformed when necessary to standardize hashCode.

    • 构造器详细资料

      • GraphKeyTypeTransform

        public GraphKeyTypeTransform(long vertexCount)
        Create a key type transform. The type is configured by the command-line arguments but because many types reduce the size of the vertex ID space the maximum extent must be set explicitly by the input in order to perform bounds checking. An n-bit type can store up to 2^n - 1 vertex identifiers.
        参数:
        vertexCount - the size of the vertex set of the input graph
